data.description: Welcome to your dream retreat nestled on a 1.5-acre canvas of nature's finest! This enchanting brick ranch residence offers an inviting sanctuary for those seeking tranquility while still be closing to town. The heart of the home is a chef's delight, boasting stunning granite countertops and a brand new dishwasher. The rejuvenated bathroom features a resurfaced bathtub and surround with new luxury vinyl plank flooring that has also been installed in the kitchen and laundry room.  All 3 bedrooms have new neutral carpet.  Hardwoods in the living areas and hall will be refinished for the new buyer of this home at closing.  This remarkable property not only features an attached 2-car garage but also offers a detached garage, providing ample space for vehicles, hobbies, or additional storage needs. With this extra space, the possibilities are endless. Seller motivated and says bring an offer!
